Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.92,0:03:12.10,Mainstyle,K,0000,0000,0000,,Yomi…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.10,0:03:13.17,Mainstyle,K,0000,0000,0000,,Otče…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.94,0:03:19.51,Mainstyle,K,0000,0000,0000,,Přestaňte.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.51,0:03:21.43,Mainstyle,K,0000,0000,0000,,Nebojujte spolu.
